response.original_title: Diane Schuur: Live from Seattle - with Maynard Ferguson and His Big Bop Nouveau Band
response.overview: This DVD features Diane Schuur performing 15 tunes with Big Bop Nouveau (including fan favorite Carl Fischer). The final two songs (Just Friends and It Don't Mean A Thing If It Ain't Got That Swing) are performed with Maynard. It's a delight to hear Diane and Maynard trade riffs, with Diane occasionally mimicking Maynard's exuberant sound. Diane Schuur comments, "I had a blast working with Maynard and his power packed band.
response.title: Diane Schuur: Live from Seattle - with Maynard Ferguson and His Big Bop Nouveau Band
